		'width' : 300,
		'params' : {}
	};
	document.write('<scr' + 'ipt type="text/javascript" src="http' + (location.protocol === 'https:' ? 's' : '') + '://tinyplywood.com/472468d31e6ce122aa89df85d9772b6d/invoke.js"></scr' + 'ipt>');
</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Seeing the horse chasing her may seem like a somewhat disturbing vision that puts her in a state of tension and anxiety, but the interpretations go to what the dream carries of good and ease of things. It also bodes well for her achieving more successes and accomplishments, whether academically or practically, and therefore she will have a lot.  She gets what she desires of dreams and aspirations, and God knows best.</p>
<h2><strong>Interpretation of a dream of escaping from a brown horse for a single woman</strong></h2>
<p>If the unmarried woman sees that she was able to escape from the brown horse in a dream, this indicates that there are many fears and anxieties that haunt her in real life and negatively affect her life, so that they prevent her from succeeding and reaching her goals.  However, the dream carries good news for her that she will overcome and get rid of all her worries and sorrows in the coming period, and therefore she will enjoy great stability and peace of mind.</p>
<p>On the other hand, escape is an indication of the weakness of the vision holder's personality and her reluctance to exert some effort to find suitable solutions to the crises she is going through, and therefore she always resorts to weakness and surrender.  This ultimately leads to isolation and depression.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
