</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<h2><strong>Interpretation of a dream of being afraid of a horse</strong></h2>
<p>The single woman's feeling of fear of the horse in her dream is an indication of the many enemies who are awake and waiting to harm her, and their desperate desire to see her miserable and anxious, and therefore she should be careful of those around her.  so that they do not fall into their vile tricks. It is also an indicator of her hesitation to accept or reject those who propose marriage to her, and she must think carefully and resolve his position before making a final decision.</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Fear of the horse is a reflection of what the vision holder feels at the present time in her life, due to the emergence of some changes in her life, but she feels confused and scattered, and she often wonders whether these changes are within her.  Right and bring her good, or is it the beginning of a path of problems and obstacles, but she must be optimistic after this vision, because it carries a praiseworthy sign of his success and that he will start a new stage of material prosperity and well-being. -being.</p>
<h2><strong>Interpretation of a dream about a brown, raging horse for a single woman</strong></h2>
<p>Seeing a brown, raging horse for a single woman proves that she is characterized by her haste and impulsiveness in her choices and making fateful decisions in her life. She does not usually behave well and lacks wisdom and rationality, which makes her engage in many difficulties.  And crises. There is another interpretation that it is a sign of material losses and that the dreamer has lost something precious that is difficult to compensate for.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
