</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>The oven in a dream indicates work in a factory or plant. Whoever sees that they have an oven in the winter, while its fire warms them, and shows them clothes, comfort, and benefits, it also indicates that they may travel and <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-أكل-الفاكهة-في-المنام?page=501" > eat fruit </a> at an inappropriate time.<br/>And if it is summer, then it indicates illnesses from heat and blood flow, worries, and difficulties. Perhaps the oven indicates the stomach due to the food and drink that are placed in it.</p>
<p>Whoever sees that they have put their head in an oven will be accompanied by someone who is of no benefit. Also, whoever sees that they have put their head in a clay oven in their dream, this means that they will do what they should not do.</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of the Oven in a Dream according to <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a></span></h2>
<p><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a> mentioned that the oven in a dream indicates the belly, where many things fly. And whoever sees that their oven is torn or has a defect or problem, this indicates that they will get stomach illnesses.<br/>And <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a> said: Whoever sees the oven in a dream, it indicates that they will enter a new job and earn a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-الكثير-من-المال-لابن-سيرين?page=1849" > lot of money </a> from it.<br/>Whoever sees that the oven is in the house in a dream, this indicates a change in their situation and the end of financial crises and an improvement in the financial circumstances of the dreamer.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
