</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>When a person gets a new oven in their dream, it means that there will be a good change coming your way, which you should appreciate and accept easily and with grace.<br/>When you see that there is still heat under the oven, even though you have finished using it, this indicates the depletion of energy or intentions, or that you will stop working or stop a project you were working on.</p>
<p>If you see yourself making bread from scratch and putting it in the oven, it indicates a desire to achieve good and abundance in your life, or that you want to participate in business ventures that bring you money without much effort, or that you want to take advantage of the capital available to you and <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-كسب-المال-في-المنام?page=3081" > make money </a> for yourself.</p>
<p>If you find yourself near a hot oven in a dream, this means that you are connected to a balanced and strong relationship that could end in marriage.<br/>Seeing <strong>a broken oven being repaired in a dream</strong> indicates the repair of some relationships that were not going well with some people close to you.<br/>If you are burned by the fire of the oven in a dream, this indicates your involvement in unnecessary matters that will only bring you problems, troubles, and a bad reputation.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
