</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>The gas stove in a dream indicates unplanned pregnancy.<br/><strong>Lighting the oven in a dream</strong> expresses doubt in love.<br/>A broken, cracked, or extinguished oven in a dream indicates problems at work.<br/>The presence of a well-working oven and baking food in it successfully in your dream indicates a stable relationship.</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of the Oven in a Dream for a Man</span></h2>
<p>Seeing the oven in a man's dream indicates a new beginning in a new job. Through this job, the dreamer will get a high salary.<br/>If the man sees the oven, he should take care of his capital and use it in the ideal way, especially since the dreamer is going through a good and suitable time to start a new project that brings you a lot of good.</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of the Oven in a Dream for a Pregnant Woman</span></h2>
<p>Seeing the oven in a <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-الحامل-لابن-سيرين?page=691" > pregnant woman's </a> dream indicates that the child will be a righteous son and will bring good with him, God willing.<br/>If the <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-الحامل-لابن-سيرين?page=691" > pregnant woman </a> sees that she is burned in a dream, this means that she will face health problems and difficulties during pregnancy.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
