<p>Dreaming of losing your way indicates that achieving desires will be difficult. There are other interpretations as well. We will explain it for the unmarried, the married, the pregnant, the divorced, and for the man, like a shadow, losing a way, confusion, or losing the missing on the dark road, or losing the girl and finding the way after losing her in an unknown city, according to <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a> and Imam al-Sadiq and others:</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of Losing Your Way in a Dream</span></h2>
<p>Dreaming that you are lost in the street means that you doubt everyone's intentions and that you need to listen to others to find out who has the right intentions. This dream is also a sign of self-love and indicates high self-confidence.<br/>If someone <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-شخص-ما-في-المنام?page=2395" > got lost </a> in a dream on the road, and the road was straight, this indicates his inclination towards truth and guidance. It also indicates fulfilling promises and returning rights to their owners, or helping others solve their problems.</p>
<p>Whoever sees that he is lost on the road, he participates in something that contains injustice and falsehood. If he finds the way, it means that he will return to guidance and truth.<br/>The road or path in a dream symbolizes life and a journey or a life journey. Whoever loses his way in his sleep or loses his way in a busy street loses many opportunities available to him in life, either in vain or in vain.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
