</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>The dream of being lost on the road also indicates that you can see everyone as they really are and you can discover lies or the deceptive person.</p>
<p>Being lost on the road in your dream means you will feel like you are carrying the problems of others. It also shows that you need guidance and advice. It may indicate that you are suffering from some emotional impulses and some anger problems.</p>
